# Mobile Devices
 
 - 1.5 billion new smart phones sold *per year*
 - On order of 1 phone per human on Earth
 - All smart phones have capability to be a web server
 - All smart phones can operate on wifi
 - billions of "Internet of Things"(IoT) devices also being produced
 - Consumer-owned web client devices outnumber servers by at least 10:1(guess)

